The mention of many-dimensional Euclidean space may indicate a connection to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), which often deals with high-dimensional spaces. Finally, the mention of methods providing insights into open questions suggests a connection to cs.SY (Systems and Control), which often involves finding solutions to complex problems.
